name: Three Kisses Restaurant 'N' Feni Bar

reviews.review_text:
This restaurant will take you to 90s, everywhere it’s a feel of 90s era. Food is delicious specially their Goan dishes, must try their Goan dishes.

It’s near a field area so you will find the ambience relaxing.
They have kept Color books for kids to keep them engaging, staff is polite and attentive.
The owner is very creative and joyful.

Fantastic place. Our favourite.
Tinho is so welcoming and friendly.
Tasty food. Lovely dogs. Live music was great on a Sunday. Don't miss this place.

Went for a quick lunch to this place this time in Goa. Checking their menu got excited to see Prawns caldine because we had a lovely creamy one in Candolim, got horribly disappointed with what they served. It was watery (with no flavour of coconut milk or grated coconut- only turmeric taste). Please don't order caldine here. Plus there were a lot of flies around which was a downer.
Otherwise ambience is chill with good music and there are two very friendly dogs to pet.

description:
### Three Kisses Restaurant 'N' Feni Bar: A Taste of Goa with a Nostalgic Twist

Nestled in the heart of Goa, **Three Kisses Restaurant 'N' Feni Bar** boasts an inviting rating of **4.3** stars, with 901 enthusiastic reviews reflecting diverse culinary experiences. This restaurant captures the essence of Goan culture, frequently highlighted in customer feedback through tags such as **beef roast** (12 mentions), **fish thali** (11), and **squid** (11). At this spot, you not only indulge in delicious food, but also immerse yourself in a unique ambiance that harkens back to the vibrant 90s.

### Ambiance & Design

As you step inside, the restaurant instantly transports you to a nostalgic 90s setting, with décor echoes of that era that evidently bring charm and warmth. Customers appreciate the **relaxing atmosphere** enhanced by its location near lush field areas. The photos showcase an inviting space with cozy seating and colorful accents, creating an engaging environment for families and friends alike—complete with **coloring books** for children, ensuring they are entertained while adults savor their meals. The music complements this vibrant environment, with reviews noting the ambiance is further bolstered by **live music on Sundays**, adding a delightful touch to your dining experience.

### Menu & Culinary Experience

The culinary offerings at Three Kisses are sure to entice. A selection of Goan specialties stands out, especially the **beef roast** and the much-praised **fish thali**. However, one review cautions potential diners about the **Prawns Caldine**, describing it as watery and lacking in flavor, which may suggest inconsistency in the kitchen. Despite this, the overall sentiment toward the food remains positive, with many diners raving about the **delicious Goan dishes**. The presentation of dishes shines in customer photos, showcasing vibrant colors and appetizing arrangements that stimulate the palate even before the first bite.

### Customer Experience & Service

Customer service is another highlight at Three Kisses, with many reviewers praising the **friendliness and attentiveness** of the staff, including owner Tinho, who is noted for his warm hospitality. One review specifically mentions the **friendly dogs** that roam the restaurant, contributing to a welcoming and homely vibe. The service seems to be efficient, allowing guests to enjoy their meals without long waits, although one guest notes their experience was slightly marred by the presence of flies—an area that could use more attention.

### Popularity & Reviews

The popularity of Three Kisses among diners is apparent, as social media buzzes with mentions of their lively atmosphere, enjoyable food, and nostalgic charm. Their commitment to providing a memorable experience is reflected in the overall positive sentiment across numerous reviews. While the restaurant has yet to receive notable critic ratings or awards, the sheer volume of positive feedback attests to its standing as a beloved local gem.

### Utilizing Visual Content

Customer-provided images enhance the narrative of Three Kisses. The light-filled dining area, with its playful décor, showcases a welcoming atmosphere that feels both retro and inviting. The captured moments of diners enjoying their meals, particularly the visually appealing **fish thalis** and hearty **beef roasts**, speak volumes about the culinary craftsmanship and vibrancy of Goan flavors.

In summary, **Three Kisses Restaurant 'N' Feni Bar** offers a delightful escape into the flavors of Goa, complemented by a charming atmosphere and commendable service. Whether you are a local or a visitor, this restaurant promises a nostalgic journey through taste and ambiance, all while enjoying the casual order and welcome of friendly service.
